The company settles into a new, stable state.

243
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:58,720
That final crystallization into a new policy is the update to the scalar coherence field's fee.

244
00:14:59,180 --> 00:14:59,580
Perfect.

245
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:08,760
So the contradiction of the deficit, S, caused the frantic movement of the executives, V, which ultimately resulted in the new, stable structure of the hiring freeze, phi.

